#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Place your hand on the keyboard as indicated by the 8 marked finger keys "
#| "(thumbs over the space bar) and start typing the text shown in the "
#| "teacher's line. Each key you need to press is highlighted on the keyboard "
#| "and if you need to move a finger from its resting position the target key "
#| "and the appropriate finger key is highlighted. Try to move your hands as "
#| "little as possible and after you typed a character always try to return "
#| "your fingers to their resting positions."
msgid ""
"Place your two index fingers on the two keys on your keyboard with the two "
"little tactile markers near the center of the middle character row. With "
"that done your other fingers will find their intended keys almost "
"automatically. Your thumbs should rest above the space key, the only key you "
"will ever use them for when touch typing. The other fingers should be placed "
"on the three keys adjacent to the marked keys on the center row. Keys for "
"the same finger are grouped together through their color. Try to move your "
"hands as little as possible and always try to return your fingers to their "
"resting positions after you have typed a character."
msgstr ""
"Połóż ręce na klawiaturze, jak oznaczono 8 kolorami (kciuki na spacji) i "
"zacznij pisać tekst pokazywany w linijce nauczyciela. Klawisz który należy "
"nacisnąć jest podświetlony na klawiaturze (ekranowej), a jeśli potrzeba "
"przesunięcia palca z jego pozycji spoczynkowej, na klawisz docelowy, "
"podświetlone są klawisze docelowy i odpowiedni klawisz spod palca. Staraj "
"się jak najmniej poruszać rękami, a po napisaniu znaku zawsze próbuj "
"przemieszczać palce na ich pozycje spoczynkowe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:293
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "While you type you may make mistakes and hit the wrong key. In that case "
#| "the student's line will change its color (per default to red) and you "
#| "have to hit Backspace to erase the wrong character (or characters) again."
msgid ""
"Start typing the text in the middle of the screen. The next key you have to "
"press is always highlighted on the keyboard visualization. While you type "
"you may make mistakes and hit the wrong key. In that case the characters "
"will displayed in red and you have to hit &Backspace; as often as necessary "
"to erase the wrongly typed characters."
msgstr ""
"Kiedy piszesz zdarzają się błędy, naciśnięcia niewłaściwych klawiszy. W "
"takim przypadku linijka studenta zmieni swój kolor (domyślnie na czerwony) i "
"musisz nacisnąć Backspace aby usunąć błędny znak (lub znaki)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you have successfully completed a line of text you need to press the "
#| "&Enter; key to advance to the next line."
msgid ""
"When you have successfully completed a line of text you need to press the "
"&Enter; to advance to the next line."
msgstr ""
"Jeśli zakończysz poprawnie jedną linię tekstu, musisz nacisnąć &Enter; aby "
"przejść do następnej."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<action>Display</action> the &ktouch; settings dialog"
msgid ""
"The key used to advance to the next line can be changed using <link linkend="
"\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch; configuration dialog</link>"
msgstr "<action>Wyświetla</action> okno dialogowe ustawieńt programu &ktouch;"

